### 注册用户
POST http://localhost:8080/api/user/register
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "username": "testuser",
  "password": "123456",
  "realName": "测试用户",
  "studentId": "20240001",
  "campus": "湖西"
}
### 添加商品
POST http://localhost:8080/api/product/add
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "title": "二手教材",
  "description": "高等数学上册，九成新",
  "price": 25.00,
  "userId": 1,
  "status": "available",
  "images": "[\"image1.jpg\"]",
  "category": "教材"
}

### 查询商品列表
GET http://localhost:8080/api/product/list
### 登录
GET http://localhost:8080/api/user/login?username=testuser&password=123456